# PersonalClaw Project Overview

## Monorepo Structure

- `apps/web` - Next.js 15 frontend dashboard (port 3000)
- `apps/api` - Hono backend on Bun (port 4000)
- `packages/shared` - @personalclaw/shared: TypeScript types, Zod schemas, constants
- `packages/db` - @personalclaw/db: Drizzle ORM schemas and migrations

## Key Rules

- Import types and schemas from `@personalclaw/shared`, never duplicate definitions
- Import DB client and schema from `@personalclaw/db`, never import `drizzle-orm` or `postgres` directly in apps
- Use Bun APIs where available (`Bun.serve`, `Bun.file`, `Bun.env`)
- All database queries MUST be scoped by `channel_id` for channel isolation
- Use Zod for all runtime validation
- TypeScript strict mode, no `any` types

## Infrastructure

- PostgreSQL 16 + pgvector on port 5432
- Valkey 8.1 (Redis-compatible) on port 6379
- Docker Compose for local development

## Package Manager

- Bun (v1.3) - use `bun install`, `bun run`, `bun test`
- Turborepo for task orchestration
